nodes.text: "From Puppets to Pao" is an interview by Amy Ratcliffe with creature performer and puppeteer Derek Arnold mostly focused on the character Paodok'Draba'Takat Sap'De'Rekti Nik'Linke'Ti' Ki'Vef'Nik'NeSevef'Li'Kek from Rogue One: A Star Wars Story. It was published in Star Wars Insider 173 on May 23, 2017.
